{"tid":2135227,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫院管理局主席中資背景范鴻齡：急需中央協助派人到港協助","createTime":"2020-08-01T09:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T10:28:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eab6ec7c0b87761e04cbda05c0762ba70efacf6f","tid":2135227,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:31:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200801/bkn-20200801164514272-0801_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200801%2Fbkn-20200801164514272-0801_00822_001.html&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PuyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=19fd84a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200801/bkn-20200801164514272-0801_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801164514272-0801_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200801170852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801164514272-0801_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200801170852&h=aff479a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港新冠肺炎疫情失控，中央明日（2日）將派人到港協助防疫。醫院管理局主席范鴻齡接受內地傳媒採訪時表示，目前最需要中央派人到港協助建立「方艙醫院」，以快速增加病床數量。<br />\n<br />\n范鴻齡在訪問中，舉例深圳市政府建臨時醫院，即「方艙醫院」只用2、3個星期時間，速度驚人。他指，難保香港不會有第四波疫情爆發，因香港屬外向型經濟，與全世界均有很大的聯繫。只要稍微放鬆或出現第四波、第五波疫情，故一定要做好最壞的打算。他坦言，目前最重要是希望中央能派人到香港，幫助香港建立內地模式的臨時醫院，並希望能夠建造多間方艙醫院，讓病床數目能快速增長。<br />\n范鴻齡提到，被稱為「方艙醫院」的亞洲博覽館社區治療設施今日(1日)正式啟用，亞博館有50名醫護及50名支援人員，整個場館可提供2000個床位，今日率先啟用的一號館有500個床位，預計首日將接收30名輕症患者。"},{"pid":"731a1c7bacd1799c3846819e5b0f2862200fc6c4","tid":2135227,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"好癲！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gniani3B_VI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgniani3B_VI&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PuyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=31685e9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gniani3B_VI</a>"},{"pid":"bb4f4ee1832de8e54429e7793aa9233655147807","tid":2135227,"uid":296369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"放呢條友入去做，就係等佢方便中央囉⋯⋯"},{"pid":"b23282a49f979893c091c35156a49531e34dedd0","tid":2135227,"uid":68746,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"兩兄妹都..."},{"pid":"9889768848c84d7c5c658560ad5620e7c1664a0e","tid":2135227,"uid":125727,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"完全冇醫護經驗都做到主席  幾百萬年薪 加花紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf905a237c74c2abd86938d542b23dca68253d7","tid":2135227,"uid":84751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"佢老母生到佢咁撚樣衰, 等我仲以為佢係ET黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dd961d862d1f916a9c1716edd0ad0ec6280bcc","tid":2135227,"uid":259088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"abf905a237c74c2abd86938d542b23dca68253d7","tid":2135227,"uid":84751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"佢老母生到佢咁撚樣衰, 等我仲以為佢係ET黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:03:33.000Z","msg":"不能不出聲<br />\n<br />\n請唔好侮辱外星人 替外星人謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a2698ec8e02ac652a1e1e7a12b131d9df43378","tid":2135227,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"香港醫護同香港人真正醫療未路了！"},{"pid":"1a5d4685718f729668fab24f61a333e83f131dea","tid":2135227,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"2020/07/25<br />\n<br />\n本港疫情持續，在下午舉行的記者會上，被問到有否需要要求內地醫療人員來港協助，醫管局總行政經理庾慧玲表示，<strong><span class=\"red\">現時主要是病床不足</span></strong>，已縮減非緊急和非必要服務，騰出床位和人手治療確診病人。"},{"pid":"cb607df45290ed81ca0080bba19becb55f0bbc85","tid":2135227,"uid":296119,"like